descrShort: The mean bite rate in kbit per second.
The percentage of miss sequence packet.
The mean delta time (time between 2 RTP packets) in milleseconds.
The mean packet spacing (time between theorical and the real timestamp) in milliseconds.
The mean jitter value (time between theorical and the real timestamp) in milliseconds.
The approximate mos note (voice end user quality) from 0 to 5
column8: only available for G711 codec only.
